{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know my parents, especially my father, talking with his brothers and, you know, with his brother-in-laws about, you know, the German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you know they hoped it would be the same as in 1914, that Holland would be spared.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember being with my parents on the balcony of the house, on the third level.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could see the planes come over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Living in Amsterdam we were, fortunately, not bombed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we saw the German planes come and go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it didn't take long after that, a couple days, before they really entered the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, that was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not really, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not in particular.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, you know, like I say, I was six years old in 1940, or five years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I don't remember the words, although, you know, gradually grew on you what-- what it meant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it didn't take long before they really started to, um, start putting down laws.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, you know, we, we were not allowed to have radios.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to turn them all in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to-- no bikes, all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, then gradually they started to limit your-- you know, where you went and what you did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- and then, of course, in 19-- I guess it was '42 or '43 that they came out that you had-- Jewish peoples over six years old had to wear the Star of David that more or less, you know, showed to everybody, you know, where you-- where you were and who you were.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, yeah, I remember kind of vaguely wearing it for the first time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
